cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with detecting and correcting adversarial images using image processing operations and convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves training neural networks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses adversarial machine learning attacks, which could place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of neural networks for detection and correction of adversarial images also suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves image processing, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia).
